Executive Summary
Jaksich is Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer for Valmont Industries Inc., one of the world's leading providers of engineered products and services for infrastructure, and irrigation equipment for agriculture. He assumed the position in 2014 after 14 years as Vice President and Controller of the Omaha, Nebras 
Personal Attributes and Interests

Jaksich is married, to Alice, and has two children, a daughter, Audrey, and a son, Sam who both have attended the University of Nebraska at Lincoln. They live in Omaha, Nebraska.
Jaksich graduated from Omaha Central High School 
